Product name: 3-PACK MINI Hamilton Fandom-Inspired Soy Candles
Description:
This listing is for a 3-PACK of the 2 oz. MINI Hamilton candles. Individual mini candles are 7 each, the 3-pack is 18. **Please list your 3 choices in the "optional note to seller" box at checkout!** If no choices are listed you will be sent three randomly-selected characters.
See my other listings for individual Hamilton-inspired candles in both 2 oz. mini and 8 oz. full sizes. 2 oz. minis are great for sampling scents, collecting multiple characters or assembling a whole collection! 8oz. full candles are perfect if you want to fill a whole room with the scent inspired by your favorite character. 
SIZE: 2 oz. jars are 2" tall and 2.1" in diameter. Candles are hand-poured in small batches; colors may vary from photo and from batch to batch.
SCENT DESCRIPTIONS:
ALEXANDER HAMILTON: Recalling his childhood in the West Indes, Hamilton’s scent begins with Caribbean teakwood, tropical fruits & spices, and - of course - sugarcane and rum. Blended with these are masculine notes including leather, tobacco, amber, musk, black tea, pepper, patchouli and sandalwood. Lightened by hints of jasmine and vanilla, the scent is finished off with a touch of - what else? - new money. 
ANGELICA SCHUYLER: Reflecting her qualities of femininity and badassery, as well as her status as the Best Sister Ever, Angelica's fragrance is both lovely and mysterious. Smoky black cherry mixes with sweet crème anglaise, deepened by sandalwood, amber and musk. 
ELIZA HAMILTON: Fit for a character too pure and perfect for this world, Eliza's fragrance is a beautiful, elegant blend of dusty rose, vanilla, cashmere and amber, mixed with a subtle underscent of paper smoke, because Lin-Manuel wants to break your heart. 
...AND PEGGY: Peggy's scent is a sweet, innocent floral fit for the youngest sister. The bouquet opens with jasmine blossoms, blended with other sweet florals like violet and gardenia. These are brightened with a hint of grapefruit, mixed with vanilla and white woods. 
JOHN LAURENS: Laurens' scent is straight-up cinnamon bun. If you don't know why, ask Tumblr. 
LAFAYETTE: Lafayette's fragrance begins with a lush bed of French Lavender, deepened by masculine notes of amber, black myrrh, vanilla, tonka bean, Egyptian musk and clary sage. 'Ow you say? - sexy! 
HERCULES MULLIGAN: In homage to his occupation as a tailor, Kool Herc's fragrance opens with notes of clean cotton and linen brightened by fresh ozone and cashmere. These elements are balanced by deeper, masculine elements of sandalwood, patchouli, musk, amber, and an unexpected touch of chocolate. Blended seamlessly with these are hints of jasmine and white blossoms.
KING GEORGE III: The royal Rickroll of the show, he's never gonna give us up. His Royal Madness's scent is fit for a king: red velvet flower mixed with plum, jasmine and a touch of patchouli. 
AARON BURR: Suggesting the dueling ground on a misty morning, Burr's fragrance includes warm woods like cedar and oak blended with soft florals. Sweet amber, vanilla and musk mingle with the ominous scent of gunpowder hanging in the air. 
MARIA REYNOLDS: Maria walks into Hamilton's life in a hot red dress hiding a scheme cold as ice. Maria's fragrance opens with floral notes of jasmine, spiced up with citrus, patchouli, cedar, sandalwood, vanilla, musk and amber. Super-sexy and smells like trouble.
GEORGE WASHINGTON: As complex as the man himself, Washington's fragrance includes cherry wood, cedar, tobacco, green fig, vanilla and honey.  
Label art by the amazing Amelia Allore at http://mimiadraws.tumblr.com/
Safety Information: To prevent fire:
- Trim wick to 1/4" before EACH burn
- Never leave candle unattended
- Keep away from children
- Keep away from combustables
See the About link for more information and candle safety tips!

-DESCRIPTION OF SCENTS-
Lemon  Clove: 
The mouth-watering aroma of warm lemon pound cake! Our Lemon Pound Cake Fragrance oil combines fresh bakery notes of yellow pound cake with a sweet lemon glaze and a hint of warm vanilla.
Vanilla  Sandalwood:
A complex herbal blend infused with six essential oils. Egyptian Amber has a rich base of vanilla, musk and sandalwood well balanced by lively top notes of jasmine, lavender and orange. 
Salt  Sea:
Great as a masculine or feminine scent, our Salt  Sea is a woody, earthy mix of vanilla and sandalwood, warmed with musk and a touch of patchouli for a calming and long lasting fragrance oil.
Blackberry  Vanilla:
Our version of this popular fragrance is fruity without being too sweet. The brightness of the ripe black raspberries is well balanced by a mellow and natural vanilla note, making this a versatile, all-year fragrance.
Fresh Squeeze:
A true-to-life blend of ripe, tangy grapefruit and mangosteen, an exotic fruit that is citrusy and sweet with a hint of peach. The fragrance reaches balance while burning, when both fruits meld into a strong fragrance that has a citrus punch, a hint of peach, and a naturally derived sweetness.
Apples  Maple Bourbon: 
Fresh apples blend in a touch of vanilla, maple, and a punch of smooth bourbon. 
Brandied Pear: 
A sweet indulgence of ripe, juicy pear and cask aged brandy. 
Green Tea  Lemongrass:
This bright and natural smelling citrus begins with a top note of orange Valencia, bergamot tea and plum wine. The heart combines jasmine, violet, lavender and orange flowers. The dry down is a clean citrus musk. 
Pumpkin Soufflé:
A true-to-life fragrance bursting with fresh pumpkin. Mouthwatering notes of butter, sugar, and spices complete this irresistible bakery fragrance. This fragrance oil is infused with nutmeg and cinnamon leaf natural essential oils.
Mexican Hot Chocolate:
Inviting aroma of hot chocolate with a little spicy twist. 
Sugar Cookie:
Just like out of the oven...vanilla and sugared perfection.
Cabin in the Woods:
Natural Spruce and cedar oils with Orange and Bergamot. 
Pineapple  Sage:
Pineapple Sage is a fragrant garden herb that attracts hummingbirds and butterflies to its edible red blooms. Our scent captures this unexpected and exotic blend with sweet pineapple and aromatic sage
Fresh Cup of Coffee:
Can it get any better! The wonderful smell of a fresh cup of coffee!
This candle will fill your home with the cozy and warm scent of a fresh cup of joe!
Marshmallow:
Sweet, but not too much….vanilla and Marshmallow.
Peppermint Bark:
Natural Peppermint oils with hints of cocoa. The perfect Peppermint Bark for all your holiday parties! 
Birthday Cake:
The wonderful smell of a freshly baked birthday cake!
This candle will fill your home with the sweet scent of vanilla and butter cream frosting....you can almost taste the sprinkles:)
Oatmeal- A good for you blend of oatmeal, milk, honey and almond. 
Milk  Honey- The country goodness of golden honey, buttermilk, vanilla sugar and sweet amber.
Red Hot Cinnamon- Like the popular candy, this old time favorite has a spicy kick and just the right amount of hot and sweet; truly a cinnamon lover's delight.
Mimosa  Mandarin- The top sparkles with crisp dew fruit, mandarin oranges, tangerines and sweet berries. The heart combines a medley of pineapple, mimosa blossoms, peaches, plums, fruity jasmine and soft lavender. The base is a beautiful lily and vanilla.
Cashmere- Envelop yourself in the warmth of vanilla, french pear and cashmere musk. 
Chocolate Fudge- Outrageously rich bittersweet chocolate, and a touch of cream, blend perfectly in our mouthwatering chocolate fudge. 
Honeysuckle  Jasmine- Bright and lively with just the right amount of softness and warmth. Truly a floral masterpiece!
Gardenia-The exquisite aroma of tropical Gardenia with a top note sweet and green and a floral body intense and rich truly capturing the natural aroma found in this beautiful flower. 
Rice Flower- A soul-soothing fragrance, softly scented rice flower.
Dahlia  Lychee- Juicy lychee, crisp apple and peach nectar blend effortlessly with a beautiful floral bouquet.
Lavender  Honey Lemon:
Perfect Blend of relaxing Lavender and fresh lemon.
Wild Rose  Honey: Warm and sweet with the scent of pure, raw honey infused with fresh rose petals.
Scent of Christmas:
Combining clementines, cloves and Fir needles and juniper., it’s the candle equivalent of a big, warm winter’s hug.

ABOUT THE WRITING / CALLIGRAPHY SUPPLY COLLECTION
Fine letter writing is becoming a lost art and yet, hand-written letters, documents, books & other hand written artifacts have contributed so vitally to preserving all of human history.
Texting and emailing is making most of modern written communication forever lost in cyperspace. This scares Bonnie (and she thinks a host of other people) so she is gradually assembling a collection of fine writing papers and accessories to give you that nice blank canvas and the tools needed to enjoyably keep this art (and your own personal history) alive.
